display="inline"><![CDATA[u-v=\vec {0}_{V}]]></fr:tex>, which means (by adding <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[v]]></fr:tex> to both sides) <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[u=v]]></fr:tex>. Hence <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[L]]></fr:tex> is injective.</fr:p><html:span
